<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-01-23 09:29:52.284586</lastBuildDate><item><title>I can’t draw but I consider this my art. Restored a classic Stingray in my garage.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Dxwlr90</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ioPz70O.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Day 1. She needs lots of body repair and some mechanical work.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D0RXG9k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Teaching myself fiberglass repair then applying it in small pieces around the entire body. Very satisfying work.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AJfL3sB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Most effort actually went underneath this bumper to reseat and bond the two panels before fixing fiberglass.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LCL0Ni5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Brake repair. Everything had to go to remove brake lock gremlins.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QilfKL5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pneumatic headlight system overhaul.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LdmTQNf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Some minor interior aesthetic work to test future looks. Some people call this wasted effort, I call it fun.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OcdEfkT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wheel strip/repaint day.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CWfhSgd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Covering up unsightly body lines.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lku9AKy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Testing paint skills learned via YouTubeU. Priming for paint wasn’t too bad.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bo6H5KA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Primer day. Low humidity, high temp.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/j0sbADK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She’s one shade and has no body holes!!!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4Qpx7Yd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Post wet-sand and first coat of paint.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JH43ry6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(Mostly) finished!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/P6TxA8d.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She turns heads.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4Mgq3JU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A small city cruise with proper music on the radio.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Dxwlr90</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[iCommunicateInGifs]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Imagine being this insecure</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/T5wvq0m</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tHlaItW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't ever want kids myself but if you have kids, you make damn sure they know you love them and are proud of them.

