TA[1Ofold]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OFyueRR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kvo4hQI.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OFyueRR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[lifonaut]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Things I will miss</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hKWejXz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BwHUlbI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My mom doesn't know how to send memes in a text message so when she finds one and thinks of me she emails it to herself puts it in a word document and takes a picture of it to send to me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kxfVx3c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I absolutely love it. I haven't taught her how to send it directly to me because I love it so much.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4uLuiM1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Honestly don't think memes would be a thing if we all had to do that.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eX68tda.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I will really miss getting these memes when she is gone. (She is 71)

Fp edit.
